                <head>No. 1367<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Representatives of the United States and Egyptian Governments signed and thereby
                    brought into force an agreement to exempt relief supplies and equipment from
                    Egyptian importation duties and from internal taxation on October 30, 1954. For
                    the text, see TIAS No. 3119, 5 <gloss target="#t_UST1">UST</gloss> (pt. 3)
                    2551.</p>
            </div>
